---
title: Baked Pork & Mushroom Cannelloni with Tomato & Basil Bruschetta
description: This dish is wrapped and stacked with juicy flavours that we can’t get enough of. Cannelloni has been stuffed with a tomato-based pork filling with pops of mushroom in every bite to make your mouth water. Enough waiting, let’s eat!
